sentence: [lip_smack] what are the cheapest first class tickets available for one way flights from new york to miami

SELECT DISTINCT  v0.one_direction_cost, '"'||v0.round_trip_required||'"',
 '"'||v9.fare_basis_code||'"', '"'||v9.class_type||'"',
 '"'||v10.fare_id||'"', '"'||v11.flight_id||'"', '"'||v12.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v13.city_code||'"', '"'||v13.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v14.airport_code||'"', '"'||v15.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v15.city_name||'"' FROM fare v0, fare_basis v9,
 flight_fare v10, flight v11, airport_service v12, city v13,
 airport_service v14, city v15 
WHERE (((v0.one_direction_cost = (
SELECT MIN (v1.one_direction_cost) FROM fare v1 
WHERE ((v1.round_trip_required = 'NO') 
AND ((v1.fare_basis_code IN (
SELECT v2.fare_basis_code FROM fare_basis v2 
WHERE (v2.class_type = 'FIRST'))) 
AND (v1.fare_id IN (
SELECT v3.fare_id FROM flight_fare v3 
WHERE (v3.flight_id IN (
SELECT v4.flight_id FROM flight v4 
WHERE ((v4.from_airport IN (
SELECT v5.airport_code FROM airport_service v5 
WHERE (v5.city_code IN (
SELECT v6.city_code FROM city v6 
WHERE (v6.city_name = 'NEW YORK'))))) 
AND (v4.to_airport IN (
SELECT v7.airport_code FROM airport_service v7 
WHERE (v7.city_code IN (
SELECT v8.city_code FROM city v8 
WHERE (v8.city_name = 'MIAMI')))))))))))))) AND (v0.round_trip_required = 'NO')) 
AND (((v0.fare_basis_code = ANY v9.fare_basis_code) 
AND (v9.class_type = 'FIRST')) AND ((v0.fare_id = ANY v10.fare_id) 
AND ((v10.flight_id = ANY v11.flight_id) 
AND (((v11.from_airport = ANY v12.airport_code) 
AND ((v12.city_code = ANY v13.city_code) AND (v13.city_name = 'NEW YORK'))) 
AND ((v11.to_airport = ANY v14.airport_code) 
AND ((v14.city_code = ANY v15.city_code) AND (v15.city_name = 'MIAMI'))))))));
